name: "HOLY GRAIL"
description:
Holy Grail is a glitter bomb topper made up of different size & shape gold glitters with subtle iridescent specks.

“…And baby, it's amazing I'm in this maze with you, I just can't crack your code/One day you screaming you love me loud, the next day you're so cold/ One day you're here, one day you're there, one day you care, you're so unfair/ sipping from your cup Till it runneth over, Holy Grail…”- Jay Z ft. Justin Timberlake

name: "LOVE ON TOP"
description:
Love on Top is a slightly burnt orange shade with added subtle iridescent shimmer.
“…Baby, Baby I can hear the wind whipping past my face, as we dance the night away/ Boy your lips taste like a night of champagne, as I kiss you again, and again, and again and again/ Now everybody asks me why I'm smiling out from ear to ear (They say love hurts), But I know (It's gonna take a little work)/ Nothing's perfect, but it's worth it after fighting through my tears, and finally you put me first...”- Beyonce

name: "BROWN SUGAR"
description:

“…Let me tell you 'bout this girl, Maybe I shouldn't/ I met her in Philly and her name was Brown Sugar/ See, we be making love constantly, that's why my eyes are a shade blood burgundy/ The way that we kiss is unlike any other way that I be kissin', when I'm kissin', what I'm missin', Won't you listen/ Brown Sugar babe, I gets high off your love I don't know how to behave…”- D’ Angelo
